  "texts": [
    "Figure 6 illustrates the average recall rates of the top k candidates (where k takes values of 5, 10, 15, 20, and 30) for each method.",
    "As the recall rate increases, so does the number of genuine DTIs successfully identified by the prediction method.",
    "Consequently, TTGCN exhibits superior DTI discovery capabilities compared to other methods, boasting the highest recall rate at each cutoff, as depicted in Fig. 6.",
    "Figure 7 presents the average coverage for each method, with lower coverage indicating a swifter discovery of all latent DTIs by the model.",
    "Thus, TTGCN proves to be more potent and efficient than alternative methods in the detection of potential DTIs."
  ]
}